21:31.671 --> 21:36.750
In banking, mining, tourism,
construction, all regulated,

21:36.751 --> 21:38.271
certified and guaranteed.

21:39.431 --> 21:42.910
Our doors are open. The world is welcome.

21:42.911 --> 21:46.390
And is General Nyamoya the price for
