21:46.391 --> 21:48.190
What price?

21:48.191 --> 21:50.390
You keep saying this.

21:50.391 --> 21:52.251
General Nyamoya gave himself up

21:52.276 --> 21:54.830
to the scrutiny of international justice.

21:54.831 --> 21:56.150
And because of this,

21:56.151 --> 22:00.100
