23:44.985 --> 23:47.575
And set up a call with
Capi Petridis, ASAP.

23:49.511 --> 23:52.270
And with whose authority are
you making this request?

23:52.271 --> 23:55.430
Capi, I'm head of the Bureau of
African Affairs,

23:55.431 --> 23:58.470
I think it's fair to say that my
authority is all you need to hear.

23:58.471 --> 24:00.190
OK, I've heard it.

24:00.191 --> 24:01.848
And what are you going to do about it?

24:01.849 --> 24:06.430
Eunice, her name is on the list
along with the others.

24:06.431 --> 24:08.119
And what I'm suggesting to you is

24:08.120 --> 24:12.150
there should only be one name on
that list. Eve Ashby.

24:12.151 --> 24:14.470
Your suggestion is noted.

24:14.471 --> 24:18.910
